channel.title: [PI] Some items are not appear in store interface
channel.description:
Hi, Some items are not appearing in a shop. Like this: [img]http://i.imgur.com/EXGxPFs.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/dkAQVo1.png[/img]
Any1 know how i fix this :D?

item.title: [PI] Some items are not appear in store interface
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

I Smoke Kush:

Client sided I think you dont got the models.

That or the models may have been replaced/overwritten.
Spawn them in your inventory. Check if they show there, and also drop them and see if they show.
Inventory model should be the model you’re worried about tho, as it’s used in the shop.

Read full topic
